{"type":null,"faqId":43424,"title":"为什么屏幕无法自动旋转？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.s1{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.27708334in;}\n.p1{text-indent:-0.24791667in;margin-left:0.95694447in;margin-top:0.055555556in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{margin-left:0.70902777in;margin-top:0.055555556in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n <span>请确认是否开启屏幕自动旋转功能。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>打开通知面板快捷开关，点击</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=150844\" style=\"width:0.17638889in;height:0.1736111in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>，开启自动旋转屏幕功能。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n <span>使用某些第三方应用时，屏幕无法自动旋转。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>请确认此应用程序是否支持重力感应。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n <span>误删某些系统文件可能会导致屏幕无法自动旋转，建议备份重要数据后将手机恢复出厂设置或进行系统升级。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>进入</span><a href=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/cn/support/downloads/index.htm%22 \\o %22 \"><span>华为官网软</span><a name=\"_Hlt415651724\"><a name=\"_Hlt415651725\"><span>件下载地址</span></a></a></a><span>下载软件升级包，参考升级包中的升级指导完成升级。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":134,"faqType":"硬件与外观","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"8925","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Hardware-Appearance","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1442398846000,"seriesProductName":"CRR-CL10,CRR-TL10","visitedTimes":2,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"